  p:hasMother mo:Alkmene ;
  p:nativeTerm "Ἡρακλῆς"; 
  p:hasGender :male ;
  skos:definition "The greatest of the Greek heroes who was famed the Twelve Labours imposed upon him by King Eurystheus. Upon his death he ascended to join the ranks of the gods on Olympus becoming a divine-protector of mankind."@en ;
